member.summary:
SafeTimer - A wrapper class around .NET Timer objects, with some additional built-in safeguards against edge-case errors.
SafeTimer is a replacement for .NET Timer objects, and removes some of the more infrequently used method overloads for simplification. SafeTimer provides centralization of various "guard code" previously added in various places for handling edge-case fault conditions.
Log levels used: Recovered faults => Warning, Per-Timer operations => Verbose, Per-tick operations => Verbose3
